You might wonder why there is a file with a strange language to many of
you. ;-) This is what you get when you send out a beta version to a few
developers and then disappear from the scene for a while. Eric checked this
file in in good faith but it is just a "NOTES, stuff you might want do test
and check later" reminder for me which was left in the work directory. 

So if you can read german (or use babelfish), feel free to tackle some
of the tasks here. There is actually some documentation in here but it
shouldn't be too helpful for the general audience. I will leave this
here for the moment.

			-- Henning

